Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:11.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}即便天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:17.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}即便時光荏苒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:20.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}不能忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:24.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}無法磨滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:27.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}相擁而泣破涕為笑的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:31.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}與溫存一起留在心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:34.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}你的擁抱就像魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}是給予我勇氣的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:44.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}活在夢想凋零的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:50.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)}不哀嘆 不彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:57.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}因為我不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:00.75,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}無懼挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.11,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}不留悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:10.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}將率真化作包容與堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}邁開步伐的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:17.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}駐足停止的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:28.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(960,1060)}一定皆是未來的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,重返地球圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,昆·遜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,駕駛艙內核和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mazraster的兼容性如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,漏水問題已經完全解決
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,弦月船會合的船員在為我們工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧和他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,加快了滿月船的引擎調試進度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,契卡拉能出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,99 100
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ⅹ警隊出動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Poligit的數量在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是滿月船艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們決定提前出航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,以防羅薩裏奧Ⅹ警察封鎖空域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,請各位在本艦離開棧橋前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,完成手頭工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}把工具和零件搬進氣密室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}準備收工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要強行突破？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說 昆·遜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ⅹ警隊裏也有奇亞隊長的支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,滿月船將履行奇亞·穆貝隊長臨終遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,開啟回歸之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人批准你們出航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是奇亞隊長的回復
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亞隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的回歸終於起航了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,掩護昆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是執行奇亞隊長遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,別給奇亞隊長擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看…ConquedeVenus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亞隊長在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是Conque的眼睛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Conque的乘員呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,三人獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但沒有隊長的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}當局認為沒有倖存者…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亞·穆貝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,懇請羅薩裏奧Ⅹ及Ⅹ警隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對不顧自身安危
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,修補海底的奇亞隊長的精神致以哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,本艦也將為哀悼隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,行全艦飾禮 作為賤別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,燈光全開 全艦飾禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,契卡拉說得沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,實力差距擺在面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ⅹ警隊裏也有人盼著回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,奇亞隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是您夢寐以求的光景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一掃興的是G-Rach和Dharma被偷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那又不是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開讓開讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,諾蕾朵才該讓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,關掉引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們幫你著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯先生 那邊沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 林戈也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？為什麼是諾蕾朵小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她非要試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒理由做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果和私營主的Beagle相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就等著坐牢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那些環的內部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全部用巨型電池填滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓地球飛到鄰近的星系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,至少需要三個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,相同規模的能量源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我曾想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,決不能讓地球人得知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,當看到吉特團這樣的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我明白 人類這種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是不會輕易改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大約20年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,皮亞尼·卡爾達事件的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,皮亞尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital特區裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,昆珀·盧西達！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他目睹了人類在這裏的衰變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宣稱需要通過地球上的弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對人類進行強化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,宣稱？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,當第六大洋迎來滿潮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,人心不免也蠢蠢欲動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可那是昆珀上校的一己之見！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你還不知「塑身衣」為何物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道實情後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也會對人類絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有看的勇氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,自己天生是個愛好虛榮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡故作堅強的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？再塗一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有縫隙的地方要塗雙層？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣底下一層的薄膜會填滿縫隙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,原來耐熱塗層是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這完全看怎麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,「我作為人類女性 健康」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 知道了　嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說 Trinity是成熟機型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這架Dahack也不是試作機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓它眼睛亮起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dharma是Dahack的翻版？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,說翻版太不尊重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它好歹和機動戰士沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dharma是耐熱機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,把這些東西供給亞美利亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你說怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,操作手冊上寫的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,歸根結底是設計師的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能樣樣實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但既然叫「完美背包」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這名字最不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他是最前線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們終歸是後方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用切這麼多的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,諾貝魯 體重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,別問 你不想聽的 別問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快說 體重計
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,比昨天0.5公斤增加 增加 增加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尿尿 尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅 你弄疼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可算追上滿月船了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的位置是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,剛過地球的靜止衛星軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,飛得這麼低？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為了和地球艦隊碰頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,通知遠古巨獸號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,全體機動戰士成員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,進入地球圈 採取二級戰備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,回到自家後院也不省心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,到底算什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特艦隊在上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞艦隊在下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍也出動了艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人跑來宇宙打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裏是環地球軌道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,減速時機晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有點偏離Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想被捲進地球人之間的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來地球是處女航
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要諸多要求！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,神轎已經降到低軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,三方勢力虎視眈眈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這時候派G-Self去第三站點瓦基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍正把軌道塔要塞化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,放心他不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了 各位小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Rach和遠古巨獸一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,試運行後與拉特爾派森碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,盧安先生 奧利弗先生 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}收到 凱爾貝斯中尉也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,火蠑螈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼近？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Lucifer的諾蕾朵·納古
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺就像在返鄉的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我和Capital塔的緣分也不淺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅 GO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Arcane 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利 背包的使用上 多留個心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,絕好的熟練機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在下凱爾貝斯也要好好習慣這架Zansgatt！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,林戈少尉記得適應低軌道環境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼小姐就不用多說了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這種大號的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,全員 瓦基拉出現噴射光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這數量…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,行動很古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,挑釁性十足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,至少不是出迎的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽還是輸給Capital軍了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,弦月船上起飛的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,必是德瑞特艦隊的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍的Ousia？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,出動這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,長竿形編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用扇形編隊笑納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,試用對消滅光子魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是G-Self嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,G…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利進入瓦基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉以下與遠古巨獸會合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解 我們去參觀亞美利亞的拉特爾派森號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,輸出功率還不是100%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是對消滅光子魚雷的威力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,塔上登錄過艾達·蘇爾坎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是媽媽批准我們入港的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她之前是被威脅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,機動部隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來見媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,來見韋米特長官的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self帶著那樣的威力回到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏的人都驚慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就不可以違反禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有G-Self和Bruzin的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,足以對抗地球以外的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,母親從沒說過要把這裏變成要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,茹甘司令知道昆珀·盧西達上校在想什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,諾頓·德瑞特將法皇扣為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,押進了神轎知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把法皇大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大逆不道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,事態早已超出我的預期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這也是人的本性使然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不 遠不止這些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我軍的面具上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,成功攻佔神轎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,此事已告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,古匈長官前往迎接法皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼他的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就作為我軍的俘虜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐是我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐父親的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,包括德瑞特艦隊依然健在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以必須如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,神轎上的面具上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,請求追火蠑螈號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要放空神轎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,貝克上尉又要出擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛差點被G-Self幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,說是因為倖存了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要去增援面具的葛蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是只有兩架倖存嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有人事後會合了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓火蠑螈和滿月船碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,讓貝克出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,冠艇還要照常運行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你看著辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就請盡快搬出這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,忙完就走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,讓面具擊沉火蠑螈號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,自己去滿月船不就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 也不問我去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,今後打算到哪裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是位很能幹的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,光是能幹 孩子可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能成為孩子的驕傲 也是好母親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這話沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父親也同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去找他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,先回遠古巨獸號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會放我們出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,冠艇的運營長官也大發雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,別胡鬧 好好站崗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信這東西是金星產的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,說你這東西是托瓦薩格產的也不靠譜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙裏裝翅膀 不好笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 少說兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特艦隊隨時會來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,回到各自崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,弦月船和派森號碰頭前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,讓瑪尼再訓練一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,拉特爾派森 近距離看好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcane返航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,直接去拉特爾派森號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦基拉上怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 見到母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,去拉特爾派森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼 準備重新出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利見到媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不能輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這次是上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒事 機體穩定多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯 盧安 奧利弗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們負責巨獸和派森的周邊警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼已經很熟練了 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,筆直向前 不找任何借口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要追上面具上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,父親剛從地球回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為了忙補給 最近經常不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,諾貝魯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她做過宇宙海盜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,盧因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,盧因·李
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在下是瑪尼·安巴薩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那算是護盾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,輸入光信號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,面具 看光信號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,巨型敵機把機體麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,請用艦炮擊落它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？是芭拉拉的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,觀它有發出光信號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能解讀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,LU…LU…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,LU…INN…LI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是「盧因李」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那架機體 絕對是友機！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,接納它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,讓芭拉拉她們撤回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}放下凝膠幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}然後關艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼金星殖民圈造的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信瑪尼的話?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,滿月船的存在讓我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,先告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是你一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,經過艱苦訓練 是我一個！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太…太好了 你平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:21:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,盧因·李！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼·安巴薩
